caption.p: Molecular docking interaction between the SARS-CoV-2 M pro and spiro[4,5]dec-6-en-1-ol, 2,6,10,10-tetramethyl. Ligand in the active site is shown in purple color, and ligand interacting with the residues are shown in blue color, pink color illustrated the residues with hydrophobic (pi-pi/pi-alkyl) stacking.
